title: Oceania 5v5 preseason tournament

embed.description: Dear Summoners, I will be hosting a free 5v5 tournament for everyone to enjoy in celebration of the preseason! Introduction 1. When is the tournament? 20th of November @ 6pm. Check-ins start at 1 hour prior to starting (5pm). Sign ups are open NOW! 2. Who are we playing?

body:
Bollockz will be hosting a free 5v5 tournament for everyone to enjoy in celebration of the preseason!

the tournament is on the 20th of November @ 6pm. Check-ins start at 1 hour prior to starting (5pm).
Sign ups are open NOW!

Feel free to join the Oceania 5v5 preseason tournament no cost on registering your team and any rank is allowed.
Best of luck on the Rift Summoners and enjoy the tournament! {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

replies.body: Most questions are answered on the main page: http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/community-events/ylatZJAc-oceania-5v5-preseason-tournament-sign-ups-open registering is at: http://events.oce.leagueoflegends.com/events/155169 .
